title: Prayer and God's Holiness {with Jackie Hill Perry and Francis Chan}
description:
Holiness. Seeing God as sacred. These are two moments from IF:Gathering 2021 that truly left me speechless. Let this episode challenge you, encourage you, and give you strength for today. This is just a taste of IF:Gathering 2022. You don't want to miss it!

Join us for IF 2022, its not too late: if2022.com
